title: 11/22: Start or Sit (AFC); Thanksgiving Buy or Sell! (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Wait until you hear where Lamar Jackson is ranked this week. But first let's do "Hopeful or Hopeless" (1:40) for some frustrating players like Jarvis Landry, Dalvin Cook and Alshon Jeffery, plus our news and notes (5:50) ... It's a holiday so let's have some fun! We're ranking all the Rocky movies including Creed (11:00) then doing Thanksgiving Buy or Sell (14:00) as we debate the values of turkey, sweet potatoes, gravy, pumpkin pie and more! ... NE-NYJ (18:40), CLE-CIN (26:00), PIT-DEN (31:40), OAK-BAL (38:40), MIA-IND (45:23), ARI-LAC (50:25), JAC-BUF (54:54) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
